## 4) Detail actions

### Chuyển sang pending zalo approval
- API:
  - `POST /internal/templates/:templateId/mark-pending-zalo-approval`
- Body:
  - không cần body

### Approve
- API:
  - `POST /internal/templates/:templateId/approve`
- Body:
```json
{
  "providerTemplateId": "ZALO_TPL_123"
}
```

### Reject
- API:
  - `POST /internal/templates/:templateId/reject`
- Body:
```json
{
  "reason": "Nội dung chưa đúng guideline"
}
```

### Disable
- API:
  - `POST /internal/templates/:templateId/disable`
- Body:
  - không cần body

### Response write action nên dùng chung
```json
{
  "id": "TEMPLATE_ID",
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "providerTemplateId": "ZALO_TPL_123",
  "rejectedReason": null,
  "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T10:00:00.000Z"
}
```

